1️⃣2️⃣ Common Production Errors & Fixes
❌ Permission Denied

Cause: Running as non-root without chown
Fix:

RUN chown -R appuser:appgroup /app
❌ Port Already Allocated
Error: bind: address already in use

Fix:

sudo lsof -i :8000
docker stop <container>
❌ Module Not Found

Cause: Wrong PYTHONPATH
Fix:

ENV PYTHONPATH="/app/deps"
❌ COPY Requires Two Arguments

Wrong:

COPY /app

Correct:

COPY --from=builder /app .
❌ Container Exits Immediately

Check:

docker logs <container>
❌ Cannot Execute Binary

Architecture mismatch.

Check:

docker inspect image | grep Architecture
❌ Root User Security Warning (Kubernetes)

Fix:

USER nonroot
